# Security Rules

## Core Rules
- Use latest Traefik versions and configurations
- Local development and home server uses HTTP (no TLS/HTTPS)
- Add 20-second timeout to all external requests
- Use kubectl for cluster interactions

## Secrets Management
- Manage all secrets through k8s/secrets/
- Use generate-secrets.sh for new secrets
- Never commit secret values
- Use base64 encoding for secret values
- Rotate secrets regularly
- Use separate secrets per environment 